    "emoji": "🕔",
    "ideation": "The five o'clock emoji represents the transition from the end of the workday to personal freedom. The performance is an animatronic clock-tower come to life. The eyes act as the clock hands: at 5:00, the hour hand is down-right and the minute hand is vertical. I simulate this through extreme asymmetry—the left eye (minute hand) is tall and high-gazing, while the right eye (hour hand) is low and side-gazing. The emotional arc is the 'mechanical tension' of the final seconds before the hour strikes, followed by a 'cuckoo clock' chime release, and finally the relief of clocking out. Colors move from industrial gray to a celebratory sunset orange.",
